The devices used in this observational registry are the Osprey Medical Contrast Monitoring System (CMS) and the Osprey Medical AVERT Reflux Reduction System.

 Both products have CE Mark designations.

 The purpose of this registry is to evaluate the usability characteristics of the combined Osprey Medical AVERT System and the Contrast Monitoring System during normal clinical use.

